fd17b27eed065377236e9c4b930da456a18","tid":385870,"uid":66618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T14:48:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嗰兩個細路本身已經一直膠開<br />\n加上成班巴迷影完曬啲散塲車，於是就去撚佢地兩個同食花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/mz9e76ya\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fmz9e76ya&h=5ceb797a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n求嗰兩個細路的其他花生"},{"pid":"e1bc20aab2fdb49e775407ac6c72ebc72d2e9120","tid":385870,"uid":54927,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T14:49:54.000Z","msg":"生仔生着巴膠真係修家"},{"pid":"86f7b1ce055b56d7ba120cec406fc31db4b85deb","tid":385870,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T14:58:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鬥屌死氣喉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n輪姦死氣喉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fe4d39be80178c931192bbbdb9614e802e02316","tid":385870,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:02:12.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n死氣喉啫<br />\n又唔係靚閪<br />\n使唔使呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為咗條死氣喉搞到咁核突，抵班友成死攞死氣喉當假閪用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edf8af4674e7c5c202511a86a4bec04756a46d11","tid":385870,"uid":113611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:03:36.000Z","msg":"其實嘈乜嘢？"},{"pid":"8b7674a591a1b3f5eb6cacecf192a78f59c13a4a","tid":385870,"uid":37971,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:04:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>嗰兩個細路本身已經一直膠開<br />\n加上成班巴迷影完曬啲散塲車，於是就去撚佢地兩個同食花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/mz9e76ya\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fmz9e76ya&h=5ceb797a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n求嗰兩個細路的其他花生</blockquote><br />\n阻人影車<br />\n拍攝技術又唔係叻<br />\n同其他同好嘅相處態度惡劣，又成日派膠<br />\n其中一個，成日遊車河都會高聲談話，對其他乘容造成滋擾<br />\n7月初最後一架無廣告嘅白板車退役，last day前幾日完全冇出過嚟做生意，係因為喺架車擺廠前行過嘅最後一程入面，佢喺度搞事<br />\n<br />\nany肥，兩個都係出曬名嘅犯眾憎"},{"pid":"e8e517678f3c418aa7bbf6bcafd7e3ddc8b775b8","tid":385870,"uid":18465,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:06:03.000Z","msg":"鍾意巴士都係個腦有問題<br />\n好人好者點會鍾意埋d咁既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42a8b0acb9b2a34814b463f3c83fd19173162940","tid":385870,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:06:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實嘈乜嘢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇片就話黑衫條友阻人屌死氣喉，所以俾人燒佢引擎<br />\n<br />\n好似係，除非唔係"},{"pid":"c9c52cb2c8a1c7768477305b2cbead53d056a5bf","tid":385870,"uid":37971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:06:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生仔生着巴膠真係修家</blockquote><br />\n我都係巴迷<br />\n但係對於呢兩隻巴膠嘅所為一樣覺得不齒"},{"pid":"7c8f774452af759140aa5e92b17decd18e77c402","tid":385870,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:06:51.000Z","msg":"果然係巴膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當時喺銀禧 聽到好大聲鬧交聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73a1cd9c1e3e3ceb256b18eee7f54a8f7ea1ae3f","tid":385870,"uid":4493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:08:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鍾意巴士都係個腦有問題<br />\n好人好者點會鍾意埋d咁既野<img src=\"/a